1.3.1 2026-06-01
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Fixed issue in wrap_geometry() when passing a LineString geometry.

1.3 2026-05-08
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Add geometry submodule including wrap_geometry() to split lines/polygons
  at the dateline and unfold polygons covering the North/South pole(s).

1.2.2 2025-07-16
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Fixed serialization issue for datetime fields: the default string
  representation of datetime fields no longer has timezone information.

1.2.1 2024-01-05
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Fixed Django 4 compatibility issue.

1.2 2023-05-15
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Fixed compatibility issue with django-filter 2.x.
  muninn-django now requires django-filter 2.0 or later.

1.1 2022-07-14
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Enabled filtering on geography types.

* Compatibility fixes for muninn 5.x.

1.0.1 2019-03-14
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Small cleanup and fixes


1.0 2018-06-19
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* First official release of muninn-django.
